                    <span>There are few up-to-datea travel books for Ethiopia, but this is as good as any other country guide. The author, Philip Briggs, does a nice job of covering the major tourist attractions as well as focusing on the more quiet areas. If you are going to Ethiopia, this is a great guide to bring along!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Must read travel guide for Ethiopia</div>
